										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You have an unused $100 Amazon gift card you want to urgently convert to cash to sort some bills. However, with so many gift card platforms claiming “high rates” and “instant payout,&#8221; you&#8217;re forced to manually sift through them, looking for a sign to identify the one that looks like the safest place to trade your gift cards.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Searching for a reliable gift card platform can be time-consuming, and choosing the wrong service may lead to lower payouts or transaction issues. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To help simplify the comparison process, this guide reviews five platforms commonly used for selling Amazon and eBay gift cards in Nigeria. These sites were selected based on their rates, transparency, and other notable features. Readers can compare the platforms based on their features, payout methods, and transparency. </span></p>
<h2><b>Platforms for Selling Amazon and eBay Gift Cards for Cash in Nigeria </b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This list includes five platforms used for selling Amazon and eBay gift cards in Nigeria, including Cardtonic, XBanka, 1MinutePay, Astro Africa, and TradeCard. </span></p>
