					<description><![CDATA[<p>Two Desperados Secures $20M to Accelerate Global User Growth Two Desperados has secured $20 million in user acquisition financing. PvX Partners is leading the investment. Two Desperados is a Belgrade-based</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/two-desperados-secures-20m-ua-financing/" data-wpel-link="internal">Two Desperados Secures $20M UA Financing to Scale Mobile Gaming Portfolio</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><b>Two Desperados Secures $20M to Accelerate Global User Growth</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Two Desperados has secured $20 million in user acquisition financing. PvX Partners is leading the investment. Two Desperados is a Belgrade-based studio and is considered one of the largest independent mobile game companies in Southeast Europe.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The financing is non-dilutive. This means that the company can grow and develop without selling equity in their business. The money raised from the deal will be invested in expanding user acquisition on a global scale. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The funds will be channeled to support the marketing of their diverse and growing collection of mobile game titles. By leveraging these new funds, Two Desperados aims to continue growing its player base. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company is considered one of the best in the casual gaming space and now offers a total of more than 30 million downloads of its games. The company plans to use this to extend its user acquisition worldwide.</span></p>
<h2><b>Portfolio Growth Driven by Casual Mobile Game Success</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Two Desperados specializes in developing mobile games centered on casual puzzle mechanics. The studio’s portfolio includes Nonogram Crossing, Marble Shooter: Viola’s Quest, and Marble Woka Woka, building strong player relationships. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Two Desperados has constantly concentrated on user-friendliness and long-term engagement. The company keeps expanding the </span><a href="https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/portfolio" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">portfolio</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> in all the app stores worldwide and has been on the market since the founder&#8217;s time. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Two Desperados was founded by CEO Vojislav Milutinovic and the company is based in Belgrade, Serbia. Two Desperados is one of the most renowned independent developers in the region and its 30 million+ downloads show it has had a lasting impact with the games it creates, and that it continues to do so in different regions worldwide.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">This growth has positioned it for further expansion. The company aims to scale its existing titles while launching new experiences. It is focused on increasing visibility in highly competitive mobile gaming categories. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">User acquisition remains central to its strategy. PvX Partners’ financing structure enables data-driven scaling. Marketing spend can be adjusted based on performance metrics. This allows for more efficient growth across mobile platforms.</span></p>
<h2><b>Non-Dilutive Financing Model Attracts Gaming Studios<br />
</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_202748" style="width: 1322px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-202748" class="size-full wp-image-202748" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/a-futuristic-poster-showcases-a-vibrant-_0xUQXpKFUjaiYzRMUSj44Q_rQFGRW-8RLKofSdqKi4F-Q.png" alt="Mobile gaming platform with data-driven user acquisition and performance marketing analytics" width="1312" height="736" /><p id="caption-attachment-202748" class="wp-caption-text">Non-dilutive financing gains traction as gaming studios scale user acquisition while retaining full ownership. Source: Created by Ventureburn</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The $20 million investment is structured as non-dilutive capital. This means Two Desperados retains full ownership control. The model has become increasingly popular among mobile gaming studios. PvX Partners provides revolving financing facilities. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">These are designed specifically for user acquisition campaigns. Studios can scale marketing investment without raising traditional equity funding. The approach allows companies to grow faster while preserving long-term value. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">It also reduces pressure to dilute ownership during key growth phases. Many gaming studios are exploring similar financing options. Founder and CEO Vojislav Milutinovic described the partnership as a major milestone. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">He said the funding will help expand the reach of the studio’s games to global audiences. He also highlighted the importance of maintaining independence. The gaming industry has become increasingly competitive. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">User acquisition costs continue to rise across major app stores. Flexible financing models are emerging as a solution. PvX Partners believes performance-based capital will play a growing role in the sector. The firm supports studios that demonstrate strong engagement metrics and scalable titles. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: <a href="https://ventureburn.com/evotrex-raises-30m-series-a-rv-development/" data-wpel-link="internal">Evotrex Raises $30M Series A to Advance Power-Generating RV Development</a></span></p>
<h2><b>Expansion Strategy Focuses on Global Audience Growth</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The new funding will support aggressive expansion across global markets. Two Desperados plans to increase user acquisition spending across its portfolio. This will help drive downloads and engagement.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company aims to strengthen its position in the casual mobile gaming segment. It will focus on scaling proven titles while exploring new development opportunities. Growth will be driven by data-led marketing strategies.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Two Desperados has built a reputation for high-quality puzzle games. Its design approach focuses on simplicity and long-term player retention. This has helped the studio maintain steady growth. The company continues to invest in product development and user experience. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">It is also expanding its analytics capabilities to support performance marketing. These efforts are designed to improve monetisation and retention. With new capital in place, Two Desperados is preparing for its next phase of expansion..</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">To stay updated on crypto venture capital funding and market trends, visit our </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/category/news/venture-capital/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">venture capital news section</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> for more insights.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/two-desperados-secures-20m-ua-financing/" data-wpel-link="internal">Two Desperados Secures $20M UA Financing to Scale Mobile Gaming Portfolio</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
